      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOW IT'S DONE (4) stalked lead from an outside box last start before finishing second (17.24) at Murray Bridge Straight in a Maiden over 300m. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Must come into calculations. CASH CARRIAGE (8) copped a check in the run last time and never threatened when fourth (20.58) in a Maiden at this track. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Rates a leading chance. SPRINGVALE MARGI (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (20.13) at this track behind White Hot Dreams in a Maiden. Has the pace to be prominent. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Bold showing expected. MICK SAID SO (2) was unplaced here last start but gets his chance to atone.",
